Lesotho’s May Annual Inflation Accelerates to 4.3% From 4.1%, Agency Says

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-06-23T08:53:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/lesotho-s-may-annual-inflation-accelerates-to-4-3-from-4-1-agency-says.html
Lesotho’s inflation rate rose to 
4.3 percent in May from a year earlier, the nation’s statistics
agency said.  Inflation accelerated from 4.1 percent in April, the
Maseru-based National Statistics Office said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Durban,  South Africa  at 
 blatham@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
